813
00:29:17.797 --> 00:29:19.631
You already are. with DNA.

814
00:29:19.632 --> 00:29:20.799
Yeah.

815
00:29:20.800 --> 00:29:22.342
I love you. man.

816
00:29:22.343 --> 00:29:24.178
