939
00:33:52.530 --> 00:33:55.532
We got you. Dad.

940
00:33:55.533 --> 00:33:58.744
Let's give you some private
time with your family.

941
00:33:58.745 --> 00:34:01.246
Thanks.

942
00:34:01.247 --> 00:34:02.873
Sorry. Thank you.

943
00:34:02.874 --> 00:34:04.458
I was worried he might bail.

944
00:34:04.459 --> 00:34:05.709
My pleasure.

945
00:34:05.710 --> 00:34:07.419
The real thanks
goes to the newbie here

946
00:34:07.420 --> 00:34:09.088
for thinking outside the box.

947
00:34:11.841 --> 00:34:13.759
Sorry I doubted
your med-surg pitch.

948
00:34:13.760 --> 00:34:15.343
Oh. no sweat.

949
00:34:15.344 --> 00:34:17.554
How'd you think of that?

950
00:34:17.555 --> 00:34:20.223
My family had to think
of a lot of creative ways

951
00:34:20.224 --> 00:34:23.268
to help my uninsured grandma.

952
00:34:23.269 --> 00:34:24.811
Leukemia.

953
00:34:24.812 --> 00:34:28.148
System doesn't work for you.
you gotta work the system.

954
00:34:28.149 --> 00:34:30.400
She survive?

955
00:34:30.401 --> 00:34:32.611
For a while. till she didn't.

956
00:34:32.612 --> 00:34:35.072
She died before my freshman
year in college.

957
00:34:35.073 --> 00:34:37.407
Sorry.

958
00:34:37.408 --> 00:34:39.576
Her death taught me a lot.

959
00:34:39.577 --> 00:34:42.455
Mainly that I don't wanna
be around people dying.

960
00:34:44.332 --> 00:34:47.000
So they got her. and we
can get out of here soon?

961
00:34:47.001 --> 00:34:48.460
Yeah.
Oh. I think so.

962
00:34:48.461 --> 00:34:49.878
- I think so. yeah.
- OK.

963
00:34:49.879 --> 00:34:53.131
Hi.

964
00:34:53.132 --> 00:34:55.717
Morphine PCA looks ready to go.

965
00:34:55.718 --> 00:34:57.719
This should do the trick.

966
00:34:57.720 --> 00:34:59.137
Do you notice a difference?

967
00:34:59.138 --> 00:35:00.138
Better.

968
00:35:00.139 --> 00:35:02.641
Oh. great. Great.

969
00:35:02.642 --> 00:35:04.392
How does this thing work?

970
00:35:04.393 --> 00:35:06.812
There's a baseline rate
of morphine.

971
00:35:06.813 --> 00:35:08.855
And if you're having pain.
you can push this button.

972
00:35:08.856 --> 00:35:09.856
You'll get some extra.

973
00:35:09.857 --> 00:35:11.191
And you can push
for another dose

974
00:35:11.192 --> 00:35:12.651
every 10 minutes if needed.

975
00:35:12.652 --> 00:35:14.821
Your very own morphine butler.

976
00:35:17.406 --> 00:35:18.573
Amazing.

977
00:35:18.574 --> 00:35:20.117
She can go home with this?

978
00:35:20.118 --> 00:35:21.660
Yeah.

979
00:35:21.661 --> 00:35:23.787
Though you'll need
more equipment for the house

980
00:35:23.788 --> 00:35:25.997
now that she can't
bear weight on her leg.

981
00:35:25.998 --> 00:35:27.916
OK.
Like what?

982
00:35:27.917 --> 00:35:32.087
A wheelchair to go to
the bathroom. a shower chair.

983
00:35:32.088 --> 00:35:34.297
wall bars. if you
don't already have them.

984
00:35:34.298 --> 00:35:37.425
And a hospital bed
could be helpful too.

985
00:35:37.426 --> 00:35:38.760
How do we get all that?

986
00:35:38.761 --> 00:35:40.637
You don't.
I do.

987
00:35:40.638 --> 00:35:42.514
I will get everything
so that the two of you

988
00:35:42.515 --> 00:35:44.724
can get out of here
and back to the kids.

989
00:35:44.725 --> 00:35:46.811
